{"tid":1253623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］［反送中］究竟各位而家想點？","createTime":"2019-06-23T16:11:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T13:42:41.000Z","uid":177213,"like":124,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"2f66ba7b9be7dc624e2f6cf04810b1a6c163fc8b","tid":1253623,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:11:50.000Z","msg":"作為一個前線義士<br />\n我明白吊頸都要抖吓氣<br />\n但究竟呢兩日各位喺度做乜勁？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌你老母成班連登仔唔知做乜開埋曬啲膠Po圍爐取暖，啲on9嘢就唔洗兩個鐘幾千個Like</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n集會活動啲宣傳Po呢？<br />\n6.24行動嘅宣傳Po幾個鐘就得嗰二千幾個Like<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6.26律政師Deadline<br />\n6.27圍律政<br />\n戰略Post<br />\n<br />\n全撚部正經野就沉撚曬底</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而家打緊仗啊屌你老味<br />\n<br />\n麥美娟講唔講粗口關你撚事咩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲敢話唔係當我哋義士係Condom?</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位喺公海group可唔可以講少啲on9嘢？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">啲圖、戰術、建議成Q日沉曬</span><br />\n<br />\n同咪<br />\n<br />\n文宣Group可唔可以透明少少?<br />\n圖呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">6.26 律政師 deadline有冇圖？<br />\n6.27 圍律政師又有冇圖？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">我知文宣組好勁好辛苦</span><br />\n不過可唔可以<span style=\"color: red;\">暫時</span>減少啲人去建制Facebook玩分化<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而家啲活動宣傳真係唔夠<br />\n求各位文宣組嘅同事放返少少心機喺活動宣傳上面</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我肯上前線<br />\n（可以用起底功能睇我啲Post)<br />\n食幾多催淚彈都願意<br />\n<br />\n為咗自由送死又點話？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過真係唔知啲活動夠唔夠人...<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日我就出硬</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又有幾多人肯響應？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔係想分化<br />\n不過對而家嘅情況真係睇唔過眼..."},{"pid":"0398f7df7700db91fcb901867f868a02142232e8","tid":1253623,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:11:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e3e5f1d9262891fda6ad49411eeeabf9c7ac503","tid":1253623,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:12:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ddc710e384012eb3a8c0463d2cea00f4d45d44ad","tid":1253623,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:12:34.000Z","msg":"各位唔該爭氣啲"},{"pid":"7f2a69dcfff4e153709fced27d1e8c900b9750cb","tid":1253623,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:12:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e136eef9e7bba34c73266396d69d3dd1ec9cf016","tid":1253623,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:13:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"76e8b61d737aaae4be787769766e15f7b67096aa","tid":1253623,"uid":156527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"聽日見"},{"pid":"43bd13208942f721bb3f50d7bbc7d44b571fbad4","tid":1253623,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76e8b61d737aaae4be787769766e15f7b67096aa","tid":1253623,"uid":156527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"聽日見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:15:04.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"df558ae4588626b8c91b2b8183044509fcf02ecd","tid":1253623,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:15:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d870424d3ece02a96800e886e3ecfebcef630c3f","tid":1253623,"uid":157994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T16:15:26.000Z","msg":"做緊野"},{"pid":"328f480ba87783e7e99ad2fc80c4d0dcdbf9b094","tid":1253623,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d870424d3ece02a96800e